# Copy to .env.local and set the backend URL to switch from mock data to the real API.
# Leave unset (or empty) to keep the offline prototype mode (mock JSON + localStorage).
#
#   unset  → mock mode (current prototype behavior)
#   set    → all data calls go to this backend (see docs/PROJECT_TASKS.md, Lane D)
#
# Example:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.fuyao-example.com
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
